SIMPLE: uncomfortable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncomfortable
<hw>Un*com"fort*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Feeling discomfort; uneasy; <as>as, to be <ex>uncomfortable</ex> on
account of one's position</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Causing discomfort; disagreeable; unpleasant;
<as>as, an <ex>uncomfortable</ex> seat or situation</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The most dead, <qex>uncomfortable</qex> time of the year.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*com"fort*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Un*com"fort*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncommon</ent>⟦br⟧
